OL,3,CLosses at P&O Ferries widen four years
OL,4,Cafter mass sackings
OL,6,FP&O Ferries remains heavily loss-
OL,7,Fmaking, almost four years after the
OL,8,Fcompany dismissed nearly 800 crew in
OL,9,Fan effort to cut costs and avoid
OL,10,Fbankruptcy.
OL,12,FThe company's latest accounts show it
OL,13,Flost #99 million in 2024, up from
OL,14,F#91.4 million the year before, as
OL,15,Fturnover fell by 8.9 per cent.
