OL,3,CLosses at P&O Ferries widen four years
OL,4,Cafter mass sackings
OL,6,FFreight volumes declined and passenger
OL,7,Fnumbers also slipped. P&O carried 4.3
OL,8,Fmillion passengers in 2024, down
OL,9,Fslightly on the year before and almost
OL,10,Fhalf the 8.4 million who travelled
OL,11,Fwith the company in 2018.
OL,13,FThe deficit on the company's three
OL,14,Fdefined benefit pension schemes
OL,15,Fremains high at #120 million, although
OL,16,Fthat is an improvement on #152 million
OL,17,Fthe previous year.
