OL,3,CLosses at P&O Ferries widen four years
OL,4,Cafter mass sackings
OL,6,FIn March 2022, P&O Ferries sacked its
OL,7,Fmainly British crews and replaced them
OL,8,Fwith cheaper agency staff from
OL,9,Foverseas, paying some as little as
OL,10,F#4.87 an hour.
OL,12,FThe company's chief executive at the
OL,13,Ftime, Peter Hebblethwaite, repeatedly
OL,14,Fargued that P&O would have collapsed
OL,15,Fwithout the sackings and cuts to the
OL,16,Fwage bill. He resigned in September
OL,17,Flast year.
OL,19,FThe accounts show Mr Hebblethwaite was
OL,20,Fpaid #620,000 for his final full year
OL,21,Fin charge.
