OL,3,CLosses at P&O Ferries widen four years
OL,4,Cafter mass sackings
OL,6,FFollowing widespread condemnation of
OL,7,FP&O's actions, the UK and French
OL,8,Fgovernments changed the law in 2024 to
OL,9,Frequire ferry operators to pay the
OL,10,Fminimum wage in their territorial
OL,11,Fwaters.
OL,13,FThose changes are expected to push up
OL,14,FP&O's costs further.
OL,16,FThe company continues to rely on
OL,17,Ffinancial support from its owner, DP
OL,18,FWorld, the Dubai-based ports and
OL,19,Flogistics group.
