OL,3,CLosses at P&O Ferries widen four years
OL,4,Cafter mass sackings
OL,6,FBy the end of 2024, P&O Ferries had
OL,7,Fborrowed #449 million from its parent
OL,8,Fcompany, up from #295 million a year
OL,9,Fearlier. The loan is not currently
OL,10,Fbeing repaid and is accruing interest.
OL,12,F"This looks like a business in
OL,13,Fterminal decline," said Richard
OL,14,FMurphy, emeritus professor of
OL,15,Faccounting at the University of
OL,16,FSheffield.
