OL,6,F"As to funding, the entire activity of
OL,7,Fthe company would be insolvent without
OL,8,Fthe support of its Dubai-based parent
OL,9,Fcompany. On any rational economic
OL,10,Fbasis, it is hard to see how any
OL,11,Finvestor could claim this is a viable
OL,12,Fbusiness as it is currently managed."
OL,14,FP&O has been loss-making since 2020,
OL,15,Fwhen the pandemic severely disrupted
OL,16,Ftravel and trade.
