OL,3,CLosses at P&O Ferries widen four years
OL,4,Cafter mass sackings
OL,6,FThe wider ferry industry is facing
OL,7,Frising costs from tougher regulation,
OL,8,Fhigher carbon charges and more onerous
OL,9,Fpost-Brexit border controls.
OL,10,FCompetition is fierce but rivals
OL,11,Fincluding Irish Ferries, Stena and
OL,12,FDFDS reported profits in 2024.
OL,14,FP&O's accounts show DP World has
OL,15,Fprovided a formal letter of support,
OL,16,Fcommitting to fund the company's
OL,17,Flosses for at least another year.
