OL,6,FIn a statement, P&O Ferries said: "Our
OL,7,F2024 results show that our
OL,8,Ftransformation is delivering. Despite
OL,9,Fchallenges in the freight market and
OL,10,Fthe long-term impact of Brexit on the
OL,11,Fsector, our financial position has
OL,12,Fcontinued to improve, customer
OL,13,Fsatisfaction is rising, and our state-
OL,14,Fof-the-art hybrid vessels on the
OL,15,FChannel are delivering significant
OL,16,Freductions in carbon emissions."
